The '''damutek of the eighth cortex''' was a [[damutek]] that had been grown for use by the [[Shaper caste|shapers]] who had been assigned to work with [[Nen Yim]], in order to fill the eighth cortex of [[shaping protocol]]s. The damutek was guarded at all times by a platoon of [[Warrior caste|Warriors]], both to keep intruders from getting in, and to prevent the shapers from getting out. When [[Supreme Overlord]] [[Shimrra Jamaane|Shimrra]] originally arrived on [[Coruscant/Legends#Yuuzhan'tar|Yuuzhan'tar]], the damutek was located quite some distance outside the [[Sacred Precinct]]. However, by [[29 ABY/Legends|29 ABY]], the damutek had been moved to the same compound as [[Shimrra's Citadel]]. The damutek was attacked when the [[Jedi Knight/Legends|Jedi Knights]] [[Corran Horn/Legends|Corran Horn]] and [[Tahiri Veila]] arrived to "kidnap" Nen Yim, in an attempt to take her to [[Zonama Sekot/Legends|Zonama Sekot]].

